text: Tracking stuck in Osaka Japan since Sep 7th. I called UPS and an agent said the last update was at Connecticut, Sep 21st which is different than the online tracking. I still can't get an estimated delivery date from UPS. Can someone look into it? @UPSHelp @UPS #upsdelay #UPS
@Nori_Studio Thank you for reaching out! I'd be happy to look into that for you. Please DM me your tracking number. Thanks again! https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
@UPSHelp Thanks! Just DM you the tracking number!

We got a timely response from UPS: "...since there hasn't been any scans since 09/21 I would recommenced contacting your shipper at this time to begin an investigation ..." I will ask the shipper to run an investigation and keep everyone updated here. @UPSHelp #upsdelay #UPS
Update: Shipper said UPS started Loss investigation, It takes 8 days to have a result. @UPSHelp #UPS #UPSDELAY https://t.co/svrzNPim5j
